# Reference materials (photos, videos, source GLBs used to prompt Marble)
# stay local -- Marble generation only ever runs from Jeff's laptop, and
# the Spark only needs the final scene.glb output, not the prompting
# inputs. Keep the folder structure itself (.gitkeep) so a fresh clone
# still has the right layout to drop new reference material into.
public/**/reference/*
!public/**/reference/.gitkeep
